result.name: Grove Sandwiches

reviews.text: Simple and cheap food... enough for a short western snack (panini or noodle salad 👍🏽)
Nice shop with good salads and sandwiches.

Located on the ground floor, down a side street from Cheung Sha Wan Road, this branch of Grove is part of wave of newer restaurants and cafes spreading through Lai Chi Kok. It's portions aren't huge but are tasty enough and fill a hole at lunch when Western food is what you're after, at a price that's easier to stomach than Cuisine de France.
簡單，較健康的一個選擇
水準不太穩定。對於一個成日加班想食好dd人來說，買了一盤水汪汪的意粉真的很難受。是臨近收鋪醬汁不夠加水解決嗎??!!!!!!!!!!!

reviews.text: 簡單，較健康的一個選擇
Simple and cheap food... enough for a short western snack (panini or noodle salad 👍🏽)
水準不太穩定。對於一個成日加班想食好dd人來說，買了一盤水汪汪的意粉真的很難受。是臨近收鋪醬汁不夠加水解決嗎??!!!!!!!!!!!
店面細,加上現在廣場大裝,外面圍牌,路過都不發現,店內坐位少,食物質素一般,但價錢相比附近輕食店,價錢合理得多。 留意現在門前貼上紙條,內部裝修,暫停營業,未知何時重開。

reviews.text: Fully-featured mall - great if you're living nearby and don't want to travel too far.
Spacious mall with food outlets and restaurants. Right on MTR station

A medium size mall serving the local communities with some inexpensive eateries too.  Some craftsmanship stalls too.  Just 5 min walk from the nearest metro station.  Built some 2 decades ago and thus a very humble mall but lots of local characteristics.
Have several restaurants and fast food shop here. Not too much shops and therefore it is not really a shopping mall!
Basic mall for fast food only

reviews.text: 各式商鋪齊全👍
這商場雖然不算大，但食肆很多，只是酒樓已有三間。面積雖小但不算太擠廹因很少國內自由行的遊客！一般商場應有的設施它都有，所以亦算方便！
廣埸內有大家樂 麥當勞 肯德基 太興 及兩間酒樓， 一間是潮式酒樓。廣場辦公時間比較旺，也有其他商鋪及銀行， 但不多。
